section.section:
The rights granted to Commission merit system employees under this subtitle do not apply to:
attorneys in the Office of the General Counsel;
confidential employees;
probationary employees;
employees in the Office of the General Manager;
employees in the Internal Audit Office;
employees in the Office of the Secretary; or
supervisors, as defined in § 2(11) of the National Labor Relations Act, 29 U.S.C. § 152(11).
